		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Add upto 3 companions through debug book&#xD;&#xA;- Do NOT have Laezel in party or will play different dialogue&#xD;&#xA;- Use OE code:&#xD;&#xA;oe qnight NIGHT_DaisyDream1_52669b07-9584-4c9d-8219-49679811fd4f&#xD;&#xA;- Go to camp" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="2" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The players arrive to camp and start to settle in:&#xD;&#xA;~Party arrives at camp&#xD;&#xA;~One party member is clutching their head, walking shakily&#xD;&#xA;another member is clutching their stomach + collapses on a bedroll, sweating/exhausted&#xD;&#xA;~another party member is bleeding from the gums?&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The player's tadpole is starting to activate, the first indiacation thta they are transforming into a mindflayer. Think the moment when you start to feel nauseus and headachey while fluey." />
